definition: (of birds) not yet having developed feathers
details:
adjective
- (of birds) not yet having developed feathers
= synonyms: unfledged
- not yet mature
- characteristic of a lack of maturity
= example: characteristic of a lack of maturity
- not fully developed or mature
= synonyms: green
- (used of living things especially persons) in an early period of life or development or growth
= synonyms: young
